{
  "stem": "23410.4",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "In 1943, in the death brigade, it was not an observance of God or of anything.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It was more an observance to ourselves that we are still alive.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We know what's going on.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And it was the day-- the night before.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "It was the night that we were out on [NON-ENGLISH] Street in Lwow to undig the Polish leadership that did not want to join the German.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "You see, a lot of people make a basic mistake, in my opinion, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] that why in Poland were more people killed than in any other country, even percentage-wise.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Not even the numbers, because we were the highest number.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] All other countries, practically, all, and including Denmark, what everybody speaks about Denmark, were collaborators.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Joined the Germans and built the government, like the Vichy government in France.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] The only country-- the only two or three countries that said no was Poland, Czechoslovakia, and Holland.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "These are the three countries in Europe.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "In these three countries, Czechoslovakia, being known for centuries to be the most pro-Semitic country in the world, at this time, had the highest percentage of Jews killed, because the Germans took it over.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Theresienstadt was in Czechoslovakia.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Heydrich was in Czechoslovakia.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "Because the-- the countries that collaborated were the best countries for the Jews, including one of the most pro-German was Bulgaria, where 95% of Jews survived, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] including [INAUDIBLE] wife.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And this is why Shamir's wife was a leader in Bulgarian Jews.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "But nobody wants to speak, because they are Eastern.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "You know, West is different.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] This is why people escaped from-- from northern France to the [INAUDIBLE] government to the south.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "This-- in Italy.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "Italians, they are separate.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
